---
description: Testing and security checklist
globs:
  - "app/**/*.php"
  - "routes/**/*.php"
  - "resources/views/**/*.blade.php"
  - "tests/**/*.php"
alwaysApply: false
---

Before completing a feature, check:

- Authentication
- Authorization
- CSRF
- XSS
- SQL injection
- Mass assignment
- Session handling
- File upload validation
- Price tampering
- Inventory race conditions
- Order ownership
- Admin route protection
- N+1 queries

Important feature work must include tests.

Checkout must use a transaction, lock inventory rows, re-read prices and stock, create immutable order item snapshots, and clear the cart only after commit.

Order cancellation must restore inventory no more than once.

Do not disable tests or weaken security middleware to make a task pass.
